item.title: CVE-2022-21241|2024-08-03T02:31:59.057Z -- plus%20one -- csv%2B
item.description: Cross-site scripting vulnerability in CSV+ prior to 0.8.1 allows a remote unauthenticated attacker to inject an arbitrary script or an arbitrary OS command via a specially crafted CSV file that contains HTML a tag.
